subscriber_tags_update_auth_member.name: subscriber_tags_update_auth_member
subscriber_tags_update_auth_member.withCheck:
(EXISTS ( SELECT 1
   FROM subscribers s
  WHERE ((s.id = subscriber_tags.subscriber_id) AND (s.workspace_id = app.current_workspace_id()) AND app.is_member(s.workspace_id, 'member'::workspace_role))))
